<section xml:id="C9.S5">
<title>Integral Representations</title>         
<subsection xml:id="C9.S5.SS1">
<title>Real Variable</title>        
 
 
<para xml:id="C9.S5.SS1.p1">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="1" xml:id="C9.S5.SS1.p1.s1">
 <Math equation-number="9.5.1" mode="display" xml:id="C9.S5.E1">\mathrm{Ai}\left(x\right)=\frac{1}{\pi}\int_{0}^{\infty}\cos\left(\tfrac{1}{3} t^{3}+xt\right)\mathrm{d}t</Math>.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="2" sentence-num-in-section="2" xml:id="C9.S5.SS1.p1.s2">
<Math equation-number="9.5.2" mode="display" xml:id="C9.S5.E2">\mathrm{Ai}\left(-x\right)=\frac{x^{\ifrac{1}{2}}}{\pi}\int_{-1}^{\infty}\cos \left(x^{\ifrac{3}{2}}(\tfrac{1}{3}t^{3}+t^{2}-\tfrac{2}{3})\right)\mathrm{d}t, if x&gt;0</Math>.
</sentence>

</para>
 
<para xml:id="C9.S5.SS1.p2">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="3" xml:id="C9.S5.SS1.p2.s1">
 <Math equation-number="9.5.3" mode="display" xml:id="C9.S5.E3">\mathrm{Bi}\left(x\right)=\frac{1}{\pi}\int_{0}^{\infty}\exp\left(-{\tfrac{1}{ 3}}t^{3}+xt\right)\mathrm{d}t+\frac{1}{\pi}\int_{0}^{\infty}\sin\left(\tfrac{1 }{3}t^{3}+xt\right)\mathrm{d}t</Math>.
</sentence>

</para>
 
<para xml:id="C9.S5.SS1.p3">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="4" xml:id="C9.S5.SS1.p3.s1">
See also (9.10.19),(9.11.3), (36.9.2), andVallée and Soares (2010, §2.1.3).
</sentence>

</para>
 
</subsection>
 
<subsection xml:id="C9.S5.SS2">
<title>Complex Variable</title>        
 
 
<para xml:id="C9.S5.SS2.p1">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="5" xml:id="C9.S5.SS2.p1.s1">
 <Math equation-number="9.5.4" mode="display" xml:id="C9.S5.E4">\mathrm{Ai}\left(z\right)=\frac{1}{2\pi i}\int_{\infty e^{-\pi i/3}}^{\infty e ^{\pi i/3}}\exp\left(\tfrac{1}{3}t^{3}-zt\right)\mathrm{d}t,</Math> <Math equation-number="9.5.5" mode="display" xml:id="C9.S5.E5">\mathrm{Bi}\left(z\right)=\frac{1}{2\pi}\int_{-\infty}^{\infty e^{\pi i/3}} \exp\left(\tfrac{1}{3}t^{3}-zt\right)\mathrm{d}t+\dfrac{1}{2\pi}\int_{-\infty} ^{\infty e^{-\pi i/3}}\exp\left(\tfrac{1}{3}t^{3}-zt\right)\mathrm{d}t</Math>.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="2" sentence-num-in-section="6" xml:id="C9.S5.SS2.p1.s2">
<Math equation-number="9.5.6" mode="display" xml:id="C9.S5.E6">\mathrm{Ai}\left(z\right)=\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2\pi}\int_{0}^{\infty}\exp\left(- \frac{t^{3}}{3}-\frac{z^{3}}{3t^{3}}\right)\mathrm{d}t, if |\operatorname{ph}z|&lt;\tfrac{1}{6}\pi</Math>.
</sentence>

</para>
 
<para xml:id="C9.S5.SS2.p2">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="7" xml:id="C9.S5.SS2.p2.s1">
 <Math equation-number="9.5.7" mode="display" xml:id="C9.S5.E7">\mathrm{Ai}\left(z\right)=\frac{e^{-\zeta}}{\pi}\int_{0}^{\infty}\exp\left(-z^ {\ifrac{1}{2}}t^{2}\right)\cos\left(\tfrac{1}{3}t^{3}\right)\mathrm{d}t, if |\operatorname{ph}z|&lt;\pi</Math>.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="2" sentence-num-in-section="8" xml:id="C9.S5.SS2.p2.s2">
<Math equation-number="9.5.8" mode="display" xml:id="C9.S5.E8">\mathrm{Ai}\left(z\right)=\frac{e^{-\zeta}\zeta^{\ifrac{-1}{6}}}{\sqrt{\pi}(48 )^{\ifrac{1}{6}}\Gamma\left(\frac{5}{6}\right)}\int_{0}^{\infty}e^{-t}t^{- \ifrac{1}{6}}\left(2+\frac{t}{\zeta}\right)^{-\ifrac{1}{6}}\mathrm{d}t, if |\operatorname{ph}z|&lt;\frac{2}{3}\pi</Math>.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="3" sentence-num-in-section="9" xml:id="C9.S5.SS2.p2.s3">
In (9.5.7) and (9.5.8)
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="4" sentence-num-in-section="10" xml:id="C9.S5.SS2.p2.s4">
<Math mode="inline" xml:id="C9.S5.SS2.p2.m1">\zeta=\frac{2}{3}z^{\ifrac{3}{2}}</Math>.
</sentence>

</para>
 
<para xml:id="C9.S5.SS2.p3">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="11" xml:id="C9.S5.SS2.p3.s1">
See also (9.10.18) and (9.11.4).
</sentence>

</para>
 
